      "writtenOn": "2015-10-16T01:11:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Wow, I didn\u0027t realize that they were ok with names not having the \"lib\" prefix, but this is not your ordinary shared object either. My comment about the /lib/ dir part is the left hand side of the cp operation. I see mine is in lib64/LLVMgold.so, instead of lib/LLVMgold.so.",
      "parentUuid": "fc35b4bb_292b2d1b",
      "revId": "142de256907367dfd0eb5fa4c75ac921351ffe1e",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
